description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ESSEX PARTNERSHIP UNIVERSITY NHS FOUNDATION TRUST&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;West Essex Adult Speech and language Therapy Community Services&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Speech and Language Therapist Band 6 (Band 5 Developmental Post also considered) &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Would you like to work in a dynamic and transformative team of community health and care professionals caring for patients in West Essex? Are you Open, Empowering and Caring? If so this could be the job for you!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a speech and language therapist to join our small friendly community speech and language therapy team, who provide communication and dysphagia support to adults with acquired difficulties, and their carer’s, throughout West Essex. Our varied caseload includes neurological conditions, mental health and end of life and we offer a variety if interventions including LSVT and carer training. The candidate can also have the opportunity to work with voice and head and neck patients if desired. We have a robust triage and waiting list system enabling timely intervention and we use an integrated IT patient note system ensuring we are embedded in integrated care involving GPs, Community Nursing, Specialist Support Nurses/Teams and AHP’s.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Patients are provided with a service in a variety of settings appropriate to their needs ie care homes, patients home, outpatient clinics, community inpatient wards. We have strong links with acute speech and language therapy services for CPD, Videofluoroscopy and ensuring timely transferring of patients between primary and secondary care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We can offer exceptional education, training and development opportunities .&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Car driver essential&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;EPUT are looking for motivated staff who shares our Trust values of Open, Compassionate and Empowering. In return, EPUT can offer you a range of benefits and development including;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Season Ticket Loans&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;NHS discounts for staff&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent Training facilities and opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Buying and Selling annual leave scheme&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The opportunity to work bank shifts and expand knowledge and experience in other areas&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Salary Sacrifice schemes including lease cars and Cycle to Work&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Charlotte Stadler, Team lead charlottestadler@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Tel: 07583015970&lt;/p&gt;
